    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>19世纪末。</strong> 在一条铁路线的建设工地上，发生了一系列神秘而残忍的谋杀案。从首都派出了我们——一位负责特殊任务的官员，伊利亚·萨文（Ilia Savin）——进行秘密调查。我们能否揭开隐藏在偏远针叶林深处的秘密，还是它会先吞噬我们？..</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>10小时的游戏时间 <br>根据所做的决定，主角有7种不同的死亡方式 <br>11种不同的游戏结局</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011170/extras/9c47d2d6f61b44b89f85a8ec37661352.webp?t=1740601823\" width=603 height=58 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>互动式物品栏</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含我们在调查过程中找到的所有证据、信件、提示和线索。所有可能对任务有用的东西。此外，我们还有一把纳甘左轮手枪，可以在危险时使用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011170/extras/11197388bd7cb9215c7fbfd37484ebf3.poster.avif?t=1740601823\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011170/extras/11197388bd7cb9215c7fbfd37484ebf3.webm?t=1740601823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011170/extras/11197388bd7cb9215c7fbfd37484ebf3.mp4?t=1740601823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主角性格量表</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >67个对话选项来改变主角的性格。根据回答，他会倾向于「谨慎」或「冒险」，这将直接影响故事的发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011170/extras/7bdfa4a86e0c319711d20212ef7a5d66.poster.avif?t=1740601823\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011170/extras/7bdfa4a86e0c319711d20212ef7a5d66.webm?t=1740601823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011170/extras/7bdfa4a86e0c319711d20212ef7a5d66.mp4?t=1740601823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>对同伴的影响量表</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >54句影响角色的对话。这会开启额外的对话选项和故事分支。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011170/extras/c96b9ef1dcad0171bc56b4cc4cd8c653.poster.avif?t=1740601823\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011170/extras/c96b9ef1dcad0171bc56b4cc4cd8c653.webm?t=1740601823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011170/extras/c96b9ef1dcad0171bc56b4cc4cd8c653.mp4?t=1740601823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>互动式日记</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记录当前事件的笔记。还包含所有同伴和嫌疑人的简要档案。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
